--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Release Note for VIVIECR ver.1.2.1.10 (English version)
Release Date: 2010-Dec-18
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a maintenance release with enhanced functions for VIVIPOS Application (VIVIECR) 1.2.1.x series.
Previous 1.2.1.x releases may be upgraded to this release by installing the XPI file through Add-ons Manager.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This release requires the following applications:
	- VIVIPOS OS Release 1.2.2 or above
	- VIVIPOS App Engine Release 1.2.1.5 or above
	- VIVIPOS WebApp and WebServices Release 1.2.1.3 or above

You should also install appropriate language pack (langpack-en-US_1.2.1.10.xpi) to avoid translation-related issues.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enhanced Functions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ticket#243:
Table Booking Enhancement:  You can now browse booking entries by month, week, and date conditions.

Ticket#248:
API Ehhancement: Will send out "X-Vivipos-Machine-Id" when connecting to synchronization server for visual indication.

Ticket#246:
Device Enhancement: Added EPSON TM-U220 [REDON] [REDOFF] commands

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bugs Fixed
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ticket#239:
Fixed promotion manager calculation where promotion is loss on order discount if items are reserved in promotion setting.

Ticket#241:
Set items which carry additional value in sub-items will not correctly retain the value after re-entering the shopping cart upon void sales.

Ticket#245:
Fixed sample templates where print routing was failing.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
